    • convert

      public List<org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.Bundle.BundleEntryComponent> convert(org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.Bundle bundle, DemographicData demographicData, QeAdminData qeAdminData, ScreeningProfileData screeningProfileData, List<ScreeningObservationData> screeningObservationData, String interactionId, Map<String,String> idsGenerated, String baseFHIRUrl)
      Converts consent-related data into a FHIR Consent resource wrapped in a BundleEntryComponent.
      Parameters:
      bundle - The FHIR Bundle to which the consent data is related.
      demographicData - The demographic data related to the patient.
      interactionId - The interaction ID used for tracking or referencing the conversion.
      screeningDataList - The list of screening data (if required for the consent context).
      qrAdminData - The administrative data related to the patient or organization.
      screeningResourceData - Additional screening resource data (if needed).
      Returns:
      A BundleEntryComponent containing the converted FHIR Consent resource.
